high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn right and go to the table
Pick up the knife on the table
Move a bit to the left
Slice the tomato on the table
Put the knife on the table
Pick up a tomato slice from the table
Turn right, go forward, turn left in front of the stove
Put the tomato into the pan
Pick up the pan on the stove
Turn left, go forward, turn left in front of the fridge
Put the pan in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato, put a slice in the pan and put the pan in the fridge

high_descs: Turn right, walk past the fridge to face the white table.
Pick up the knife on the right side of the table.
Face the side of the table.
Slice the tomato in the center of the table.
Put the knife on the table.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn right, walk forward to the stove and face it.
Place the tomato in the pan.
Grab the pan from the stove top.
Turn left, walk to the front of the fridge and face it.
Put the pan inside the fridge and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato for the pan to be chilled in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to face the white table.
Pick up the knife on the white table.
Take a step to the left to face the tomato in the middle of the table.
Cut the tomato on the center of the table into slices.
Place the knife on top of the cut tomato on the white table.
Pick up a slice of the tomato on the white table.
Turn right and walk across the room and turn left to face the stove.
Place the tomato slice on the pan on the front left burner.
Pick up the pan with the tomato slice in it on the stove.
Turn around and walk across the room to the right to face the fridge.
Place the pan with a tomato slice in it in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To put a tomato slice on a pan plus move them to the fridge.
